{"tid":1380252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《勇武討論》係咪有埋身機會 就要把握？","createTime":"2019-07-29T03:28:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T03:50:51.000Z","uid":66390,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"68f649c5006027565ffdc5223d578b48eb4cdbc3","tid":1380252,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:28:30.000Z","msg":"呢家啲狗唔同你玩埋身<br />\n下下玩槍<br />\n尋晚個種槍林彈雨 子彈橫飛 好明題<br />\n射撚到pan pan聲 上天花再彈返落柱 彈來彈去<br />\n<br />\n遠攻暫時唔夠打<br />\n有時幾隻速龍 防暴又唔推時候<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">係咪應該把握機會呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n廿尻幾隻速龍就唔洗講啦<br />\n但呢家個勢 好似驚速龍多過防暴咁<br />\n但防暴反而一排推 會用槍<br />\n速龍都係幾隻跑埋來<br />\n<br />\n學術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd118801076595b128d72f6a5ab6102d7ed7522","tid":1380252,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e714b407a5da14c89e3bf9b515873144ded45113","tid":1380252,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"但畜襲衝埋去防線, 全體唔埋身調頭走<br />\n<br />\n好多人被捕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1708a6a1e323c3a8b03e3057ac148888d5708551","tid":1380252,"uid":66390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e714b407a5da14c89e3bf9b515873144ded45113","tid":1380252,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"但畜襲衝埋去防線, 全體唔埋身調頭走<br />\n<br />\n好多人被捕 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T03:40:42.000Z","msg":"就係咁 我諗緊係咪埋身 會少d人被捕 咁樣退會拉幾件"},{"pid":"240a07a778000e488e2ed93914c4238cb6fc7bd1","tid":1380252,"uid":181703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e714b407a5da14c89e3bf9b515873144ded45113","tid":1